{"tid":2100158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：美律師公會表揚極權下維權大狀  吳靄儀獲國際人權獎 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-07-09T00:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T01:47:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4cd299c86c068206ee54a30b769244be595686","tid":2100158,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/KXSBV266HBVQACF2GJ6PGPTNKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FKXSBV266HBVQACF2GJ6PGPTNKY%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmk4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=88b25995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FKXSBV266HBVQACF2GJ6PGPTNKY%2F&h=07939109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/KXSBV266HBVQACF2GJ6PGPTNKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：美律師公會表揚極權下維權大狀 <br />\n吳靄儀獲國際人權獎 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eQ_EPFAe4tj4YJzWR8qyPe-JB2s=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FVBB7CEY5G4AA4CHDBGOWFW2FI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeQ_EPFAe4tj4YJzWR8qyPe-JB2s%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFVBB7CEY5G4AA4CHDBGOWFW2FI.jpg&h=7f1ebfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次吳靄儀獲得美國大律師公會之國際人權獎，受到唔少左報攻擊加持。<br />\n<br />\n香港法治籠罩喺港版國安法陰霾下，慶幸有一線陽光。前法律界立法會議員吳靄儀（Margaret）近日獲美國大律師公會，頒發今年度嘅國際人權獎，公會嘅國際人權獎委員會主席話，獎項係要表揚吳靄儀喺捍衞香港人權同法治嘅傑出成就。<br />\n<br />\n現任法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗原來係Margaret嘅提名人，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n控告佢參與及組織未經批准集會及遊行，認真諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S_9v6FCKJ8N7SxIZFEZ7wekyfCk=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JAIJYKI6GYC6UGDLBKHEUHE3HQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS_9v6FCKJ8N7SxIZFEZ7wekyfCk%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJAIJYKI6GYC6UGDLBKHEUHE3HQ.jpg&h=654d1834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方早前拘捕吳大狀，公民黨同泛民一齊出嚟質疑控方係政治檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n709案王宇律師曾獲獎<br />\n<br />\n不過有法律界中人睇完以往得獎者，發現拎得嘅好多都係一殼眼淚，好似2019年得獎人係沙地阿拉伯律師Waleed Abu al-Khair，因為爭取議會民主化，所以被控以恐怖活動罪行，判15年監。<br />\n<br />\n呢位法律界中人遇見Margaret，仲想考佢知唔知上屆得主係邊個，點知Margaret考返佢轉頭，知唔知再上兩屆得主係邊個？佢當然唔知，呢個時候Margaret答佢係王宇，709案中最先被拘捕嘅律師，聽到呢到令該法律界中人心酸。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"391ece8d6b052c981baae3b53145e6726633d62e","tid":2100158,"uid":362015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"搵唔到個source?"}]}